. keenii</em>, and each of the currently recognized subspecies of <em>M. evotis</em>, at least for those subspecies known to occur in the USA and Canada (<em>evotis</em>, p<em>acificus</em>, <em>chrysonotus</em> and <em>jonesorum</em>) (or even the types themselves for those that are still extant and in a condition that would allow for archival DNA sequencing).", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Upham, Nathan S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Francis, Charles M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Group, On Behalf Of The Global Bat Taxonomy Working Group Of The IUCN SSC Bat Specialist", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Myotis", "bat", "taxonomy", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/bdfceeffe8d8c35194fde213388c780a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/b872d17d1ba48733727ca057bf5289d0b3ee8e72f82dbeb0074fbfcfa760054f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/B25IL3RB", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/B25IL3RB", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/a77f9075b8e0953fa87e872a7bd1dec5!/b45346-47900", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"title": "Zenodo", "volume": "7336341"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/bdfceeffe8d8c35194fde213388c780a"}, {"identifier": "